Heat @apple cider vinegar{250%ml} (or white vinegar), @sugar{50%g}, @salt{} to taste, and @peppercorns{} in a saucepan until the sugar dissolves.

Pour the heated pickling solution over thinly sliced @red cabbage{500%g} and optionally apple slices.

Ensure the cabbage is fully submerged.

Cover and refrigerate for ~{24%hours} before serving.